{"tid":2393740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"業主趕移民！ 康樂園雙號屋附有私人泳池 減1000萬沽出！","createTime":"2021-02-03T16:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T16:39:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a939627c536d622d4505740d0fcce94f9324091f","tid":2393740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/property/article/id/2703788/康樂園雙號屋5550萬沽破頂\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Fproperty%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2703788%2F%E5%BA%B7%E6%A8%82%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%99%E8%99%9F%E5%B1%8B5550%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E7%A0%B4%E9%A0%82&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=419b587d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/property/article/id/2703788/康樂園雙號屋5550萬沽破頂</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2021/02/02/2703788_20a6f6ce259a27d87aaf3efc919c9081.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2021%2F02%2F02%2F2703788_20a6f6ce259a27d87aaf3efc919c9081.jpg&h=99571321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔康樂園西路雙號屋，實用面積2579方呎，擁約5000方呎大花園，附有私人泳池，開價約6500萬元，放盤約兩年，由於原業主打算移民，願提供較大議價空間，日前以5550萬元獲承接，實用呎價21520元，創同類單位新高價。<br />\n<br />\n中原地產表示，買家為用家，已睇樓一段時間，鍾情洋房擁大花園，附有豪華裝修，門口亦可停泊多部車輛，單位質素極高，考慮後即決定入市自用。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，原業主於2009年以3488萬元入市上址，持貨12年，是次成交賬面獲利2062萬元，單位升值59%。"},{"pid":"56619184ec313499e42738b0aec9b0cafaade97f","tid":2393740,"uid":267283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"房屋台專家<br />\n睇唔到<br />\n假新聞<br />\n淡友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c90aad8a34e2f7a74e11ea94f731c1fcade49d7","tid":2393740,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:26:53.000Z","msg":"減1000萬都羸2062萬<br />\nQE真係劫貧濟富<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369375d4133a1